  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the world of Silverdawn in an exciting, Hungarian-dubbed 2D platformer action game! Uncover the mystery behind the chaos and darkness that have plagued these lands. Embark on a journey with Alrik, reveal hidden secrets, and face the forces of evil to restore order to the shattered kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/7a6c34f27571d819a72dafd72b91164d.poster.avif?t=1769358526\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/7a6c34f27571d819a72dafd72b91164d.webm?t=1769358526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/7a6c34f27571d819a72dafd72b91164d.mp4?t=1769358526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/26f7cb87901eaf6feede3fdec101bdb8.poster.avif?t=1769358526\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/26f7cb87901eaf6feede3fdec101bdb8.webm?t=1769358526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/26f7cb87901eaf6feede3fdec101bdb8.mp4?t=1769358526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thrilling Universe – Traverse the lush lands of Silverdawn all the way to the frozen fortress of Isenberg in a captivating 3-hour adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blend of Action and Skill – Defend yourself with your bow against the most dangerous creatures of hell and overcome deadly obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Story and Characters – Meet a variety of characters who aid you on your quest as you uncover the secrets of the monarchy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visuals and Atmosphere – A hand-drawn medieval fantasy world awaits, where enchanting landscapes hide lurking dangers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Epic Soundtrack – Featuring music by AlkaKrab, Random Mind, Darren Curtis, Storyum, Elfsong, Zöld Bálint, Nagy Dávid, Bárány Tamás and Tales of Evening, blending medieval and modern compositions to enhance the game's atmosphere and epic feel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/3c6b9427ac719270c972bf238255e86c.poster.avif?t=1769358526\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/3c6b9427ac719270c972bf238255e86c.webm?t=1769358526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/3c6b9427ac719270c972bf238255e86c.mp4?t=1769358526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the world of Silverdawn in an exciting, Hungarian-dubbed 2D platformer action game! Uncover the mystery behind the chaos and darkness that have plagued these lands. Embark on a journey with Alrik, reveal hidden secrets, and face the forces of evil to restore order to the shattered kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/7a6c34f27571d819a72dafd72b91164d.poster.avif?t=1769358526\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/7a6c34f27571d819a72dafd72b91164d.webm?t=1769358526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/7a6c34f27571d819a72dafd72b91164d.mp4?t=1769358526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/26f7cb87901eaf6feede3fdec101bdb8.poster.avif?t=1769358526\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/26f7cb87901eaf6feede3fdec101bdb8.webm?t=1769358526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/26f7cb87901eaf6feede3fdec101bdb8.mp4?t=1769358526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thrilling Universe – Traverse the lush lands of Silverdawn all the way to the frozen fortress of Isenberg in a captivating 3-hour adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blend of Action and Skill – Defend yourself with your bow against the most dangerous creatures of hell and overcome deadly obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Story and Characters – Meet a variety of characters who aid you on your quest as you uncover the secrets of the monarchy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visuals and Atmosphere – A hand-drawn medieval fantasy world awaits, where enchanting landscapes hide lurking dangers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Epic Soundtrack – Featuring music by AlkaKrab, Random Mind, Darren Curtis, Storyum, Elfsong, Zöld Bálint, Nagy Dávid, Bárány Tamás and Tales of Evening, blending medieval and modern compositions to enhance the game's atmosphere and epic feel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/3c6b9427ac719270c972bf238255e86c.poster.avif?t=1769358526\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/3c6b9427ac719270c972bf238255e86c.webm?t=1769358526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565620/extras/3c6b9427ac719270c972bf238255e86c.mp4?t=1769358526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
